 <!--
  mappa7.tmx — Boss Arena
  240 x 20 tile @ 64px = 15360 x 1280 px
  Entry row17 (matches mappa6 exit)

  STRUCTURE:
    cols   0-119  Approach section — cave platforms, tight corridor, enemies
    cols 120-124  Transition gate  — narrow chokepoint with pillars
    cols 125-239  BOSS ARENA       — wide flat ground (row17), full-height ceiling,
                                     5 symmetric platforms for combat movement

  PLATFORMS IN ARENA:
    row14  cols128-133  left side low
    row14  cols206-211  right side low  (symmetric)
    row11  cols142-148  left-mid
    row11  cols191-197  right-mid       (symmetric)
    row9   cols168-172  center high

  SPAWNS:
    start    x1  col2  row16  (approach entry)
    Crawlid  x5  (approach section only — no enemies in arena)
    Tiktik   x4  (approach ceiling)
    Vengefly x2  (approach open gaps)
    Boss     x1  col182 row16  (center of arena)

  Tilesets: Cave_-_Floor.png | Cave_-_Platforms.png | Cave_-_RockCombinations1.png
            Cave_-_SmallRocks.png | Cave_-_BigRocks1.png | Square_-_Black.jpg
  Tile GIDs: 0=empty  11=SOLID  267=FILL  2497=STALA
 -->
